WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:03.128
I was shown the mark of the beast.

00:00:03.128 --> 00:00:16.720
I was shown what it is, and I'm not saying it's Neuralink, but I'm saying it is a type of Neuralink, what Elon Musk is working on.

00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:19.153
I'm not saying it is that, but it's that kind of technology.

00:00:21.367 --> 00:00:30.022
It's very small, but what happens is they inject it in your hand or they inject it in your forehead.

00:00:30.022 --> 00:00:39.816
Because 5G towers are not everywhere, the Antichrist, when he rules and reigns over the earth, will rule over everything.

00:00:39.816 --> 00:00:50.079
So the satellites—Starlink—there are literally, I believe, hundreds of them in the sky now, but there will be a lot more when this takes place.

00:00:52.724 --> 00:01:00.686
It provides an internet signal throughout the whole world, and it's controlled by computers.

00:01:01.173 --> 00:01:08.473
When Starlink is fully active, it will be able to communicate with the chips from Neuralink.

00:01:08.473 --> 00:01:13.960
Neuralink and Starlink will be like buddies.

00:01:14.771 --> 00:01:26.050
When they inject that chip inside of your hand or your forehead, it will communicate with the internet up above the earth's atmosphere with Starlink.

00:01:26.050 --> 00:01:43.498
I saw governments from all over the world start to use drones everywhere to look out for anybody that did not have the mark of the beast.

00:01:43.498 --> 00:01:51.200
The chip in your forehead or your hand communicated to the drones.

00:01:51.200 --> 00:01:57.326
There were drones—you could hear them—literally like swarms of bees.

00:01:58.618 --> 00:02:08.394
It even talks about it in the Bible, that it looked like locusts coming up out of a pit; I believe it was probably these drones, just my opinion.

00:02:09.674 --> 00:02:16.822
The sky was literally buzzing all over the place with thousands of drones.

00:02:17.828 --> 00:02:21.440
This is interesting: they could sense fire.

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:35.663
If the Christians had a big fire while hiding in the hills, those hills were being patrolled.

00:02:45.177 --> 00:02:49.995
But the Christians were smart and could get down into those holes and keep their heat hidden.

00:02:49.995 --> 00:03:07.954
Infrared was not able to see them, and they couldn't see the smoke if they had small fires.

00:03:14.085 --> 00:03:30.707
But if they heard a gunshot or anything to kill wildlife, those drones could hear it from forever away and would come to where that noise was.

00:03:48.750 --> 00:03:50.919
You could not shoot loud firearms to drop game, like deer, elk, or cattle, so people were starving.

00:03:59.984 --> 00:04:15.391
They would try to get fish or whatever they could find, but then they would have to create a very small fire to be able to cook that food.

00:04:15.391 --> 00:04:20.079
You run out of supplies.

00:04:20.079 --> 00:04:39.039
Try seven years—this isn't just a couple of weeks living off the grid; this is years and years of hell.

00:04:39.039 --> 00:05:00.222
I saw a woman and her two children, born during the tribulation, and her husband all standing there.

00:05:00.222 --> 00:05:22.720
They told the mother, 'If you don't take the mark and the children don't take the mark, we're going to cut those children's heads off.

00:05:22.720 --> 00:05:37.005
' As any good mother would, she was freaking out, saying, 'Don't cut my babies' heads off!

00:05:37.005 --> 00:05:39.150
I'll take the mark.

00:05:39.150 --> 00:06:01.439
' I saw her, right before my face, take the mark of the beast, and the children took the mark of the beast.

00:06:01.439 --> 00:06:12.039
The father said, 'No, I'll never take the mark of the beast.

00:06:12.039 --> 00:06:28.169
' I saw those men pull his head out, and they had a massive sword and chopped his head off right before me.

00:06:28.169 --> 00:06:36.160
I saw his head roll right to my feet.

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:47.510
I could smell the blood from the man who got his head cut off.

00:06:50.707 --> 00:06:52.493
The kids and the mother had no expression.

00:06:57.490 --> 00:07:00.319
The chip makes you motionless, with no emotions at all.

00:07:00.319 --> 00:07:03.710
You become like a zombie.

00:07:05.184 --> 00:07:10.986
It makes your mind instantaneous, like a zombie.

00:07:10.986 --> 00:07:13.279
There's nothing there.

00:07:13.919 --> 00:07:27.880
The children did not cry or wail or act upset because their father just got his head cut off.

00:07:27.880 --> 00:07:39.515
The wife didn't even act like she cared either; it was like she was not there.

00:07:54.710 --> 00:07:55.180
I saw a man mowing his grass with no expression on his face.

00:07:55.180 --> 00:08:04.808
He was in his grass, but he was gone.

00:08:04.808 --> 00:08:27.507
It was the weirdest thing seeing these people who took the mark of the beast; they were just wiped out.

00:08:27.507 --> 00:08:33.539
He was mowing but had no expression.

00:08:33.539 --> 00:08:55.630
Then I saw a man trying to commit suicide by jumping off a bridge, but whenever he did, the chip created peace in his mind.

00:08:55.630 --> 00:09:03.679
It sent a signal to his mind because it knew that hormone or thought pattern that your body creates when you're about to do something like that.

00:09:03.679 --> 00:09:14.453
It knew by your heart rate to calm you down.

00:09:14.453 --> 00:09:31.344
He was standing there, ready to jump off this major bridge to end his life, and all of a sudden, that chip caused him to calm down, and he just stepped down and walked out of there.

00:09:32.405 --> 00:09:41.760
There was no way to even do anything physically to yourself; it would not allow you to.

00:09:41.760 --> 00:09:47.560
You didn't have free will anymore.

00:09:47.560 --> 00:10:00.307
If you were trying to do anything like rioting or stealing, your mind would not do that.

00:10:14.623 --> 00:10:17.312
A lot of people want to know about the mark of the beast.

00:10:17.312 --> 00:10:28.992
I'll tell you: it's a sore, a massive boil.

00:10:28.992 --> 00:10:43.000
Whenever it reacts to the skin, it looks like a burn mark.

00:10:45.354 --> 00:11:00.200
It popped up like a boil on whoever's hand got it, and there's a black circle around that sore.

00:11:02.420 --> 00:11:08.074
It looks oozy, even the one on the forehead.

00:11:08.074 --> 00:11:13.646
Like I said, it doesn't happen to everybody who got the mark, only to certain people.

00:11:30.955 --> 00:11:31.420
It's like it had a reaction with somebody's chemistry.

00:11:31.420 --> 00:11:37.107
It's very small, a little square.

00:11:37.107 --> 00:11:45.726
It's not a grain of rice; it's a little square chip.

00:11:45.726 --> 00:11:59.863
Whenever it's injected into your body, it messes with your mind.

00:12:10.660 --> 00:12:13.479
It creates a signal to calm you down and alters your personality.

00:12:14.510 --> 00:12:35.040
I do not know how it does this, but it sends waves to your brain and causes you to be in a calm or zombie-like state.

00:12:35.040 --> 00:12:37.945
It's very weird.

00:12:41.251 --> 00:12:54.989
I saw that every single town had barricades like checkpoints on the major highways or the roads coming into town.

00:12:54.989 --> 00:13:02.959
Everybody had to go through them to come in or out.

00:13:02.959 --> 00:13:13.680
The only way you were allowed in those major cities or towns was by the mark of the beast.

00:13:13.680 --> 00:13:28.574
They scanned your hand or your forehead to get inside to get supplies like groceries, medical care, or to go to the doctor.

00:13:39.774 --> 00:13:42.970
You had to go through those major checkpoints with army men in black outfits scanning you.

00:13:55.453 --> 00:13:58.639
I saw people on foot trying to go in there.

00:13:58.639 --> 00:14:14.297
I saw a woman standing in line who had put makeup on her hand, trying to imitate the mark of the beast sore.

00:14:14.297 --> 00:14:21.760
She was that desperate to get into town for food or medical supplies.

00:14:21.760 --> 00:14:41.560
When they saw that she was faking it and they got up to scan her hand, there was no mercy.

00:14:47.879 --> 00:14:48.059
They cut her head off right there.

00:14:48.059 --> 00:14:58.074
They killed her right there, and it just rolled down onto the street.

00:14:58.074 --> 00:14:59.342
Nobody cared.

00:14:59.342 --> 00:15:04.022
All the other people in line are zombies.

00:15:04.022 --> 00:15:06.800
They were all standing in line.

00:15:06.800 --> 00:15:14.200
They would go through there into these checkpoints to get groceries.

00:15:14.200 --> 00:15:21.029
I saw public squares with massive movie screens as big as a building.

00:15:21.029 --> 00:15:26.600
By law, on Fridays, everybody dresses in white robes.

00:15:32.074 --> 00:15:35.479
You go there on Fridays, and people are in lines worshiping him on the screen.

00:15:35.479 --> 00:15:46.319
Some of it is live and some is pre-recorded because it's not daytime everywhere around the world.

00:15:46.319 --> 00:15:49.407
At the Freemasons' Temple, they worship there.

00:15:58.817 --> 00:15:59.199
I saw them worshiping in Rome, at the Vatican, and all that.

00:16:02.936 --> 00:16:06.860
They have major screens there, in Europe, in Paris—it's everywhere.

00:16:06.860 --> 00:16:11.180
Buckingham Palace had them there.

00:16:11.180 --> 00:16:14.839
I'm telling you, they're everywhere.

00:16:19.700 --> 00:16:23.759
The people are required to worship on Fridays.

00:16:23.759 --> 00:16:36.426
He creates a flag whenever he is ruling as the Antichrist over the world.

00:16:36.426 --> 00:16:48.857
He pulls down everyone else's flags, and there's only one flag for the whole world—his flag.

00:16:49.131 --> 00:17:03.680
This is what the flag looks like; I had my son create it from what I saw in my spirit.

00:17:03.680 --> 00:17:13.839
These stars represent the five pillars of Islam: faith, prayer, fasting, almsgiving, and pilgrimage.

00:17:13.839 --> 00:17:16.245
That's what those stars represent.

00:17:24.344 --> 00:17:24.679
These were like palm leaves, which represented prosperity.

00:17:24.679 --> 00:17:37.220
The swords represented something about sternness and ruling in the Islamic faith.

00:17:37.220 --> 00:17:52.091
Then this was over a globe, because the whole world was going to be controlled by the Antichrist.

00:17:52.091 --> 00:17:57.179
It was a global system.

00:17:57.179 --> 00:18:09.940
He was honoring Hamas, Al-Qaeda, and ISIS because they brought him forth; they call him the Mahdi.

00:18:09.940 --> 00:18:12.947
That's what everybody calls him.

00:18:12.947 --> 00:18:25.224
All these fields will be packed full of people on Fridays, all lined up worshiping the Antichrist.

00:18:25.224 --> 00:18:41.372
I believe with all my heart you have time to repent and ask Jesus to be your Lord and Savior.

00:18:41.372 --> 00:18:50.679
You woke up today; what are you going to do with today?

00:18:50.679 --> 00:19:02.885
I was talking to my son and said, 'There's still time for people to give their heart to Jesus.

00:19:02.885 --> 00:19:08.840
' But I'm telling you, time is running out.

00:19:08.840 --> 00:19:18.440
We're running out of the sands of time because Jesus Christ is about to come back and get His church, and at that time, it's over.

00:19:18.440 --> 00:19:22.440
But today is your day of salvation.

00:19:22.440 --> 00:19:25.360
Today is your day of repentance.

00:19:37.480 --> 00:19:37.646
You can turn from your wicked ways and make Jesus your Lord and Savior.

00:19:41.714 --> 00:19:45.099
Don't be one of the people in this field worshiping the Antichrist.

00:19:55.943 --> 00:19:56.127
I stood with Jesus and watched the people on these massive screens on the sides of buildings.

00:19:56.127 --> 00:20:02.110
You will be made to worship him here at this place.

00:20:12.490 --> 00:20:12.700
I'm just being real.

00:20:12.700 --> 00:20:21.971
People come from all around these towns in a single-file line with white outfits.

00:20:36.834 --> 00:20:38.747
This temple is hundreds of years old, but this is where they will have massive screens so that you can worship the Antichrist on Friday.

00:20:38.747 --> 00:20:58.742
If you don't believe in the Rapture and want to get left here, you can come here and worship the Antichrist or get your head cut off.

00:21:07.640 --> 00:21:08.112
There was a massive screen right there, pointing this way.

00:21:08.112 --> 00:21:24.824
On the brown building right here, you will see a massive screen one day, and the people will worship that way.

00:21:33.889 --> 00:21:39.840
This building we're approaching is where you are mandated to bring your Bible.

00:21:40.175 --> 00:21:46.560
I saw them lining up bringing the Bibles to the courthouse.

00:21:48.990 --> 00:21:54.413
They take the flag down and put the Antichrist flag up.

00:22:09.604 --> 00:22:09.946
A hundred yards away is where they will burn the Bibles.

00:22:09.946 --> 00:22:23.261
In this field right here, they're going to burn the Bibles in a humongous pile.

00:22:23.261 --> 00:22:37.960
This football stadium is like a bowl, and the stack of Bibles is huge.

00:22:37.960 --> 00:22:54.008
It's similar to when Hitler burned all the books, like you saw in Indiana Jones.

00:22:54.008 --> 00:23:06.320
That's what I saw when I was standing with Jesus.

00:23:20.559 --> 00:23:20.944
The smoke goes up for miles from burning all the Bibles.

00:23:28.039 --> 00:23:35.259
I saw massive army tank-like cars with men in solid black outfits and black shields over their faces.

00:23:35.259 --> 00:23:45.860
They would drive up in these Hummer-looking cars with blue lights in them—almost like black lights.

00:23:45.860 --> 00:24:11.013
Christians were running as fast as they could to try to get away, and the men jumped out with guns I've never seen before.

00:24:11.013 --> 00:24:19.350
People have told me they actually exist as prototypes.

00:24:19.350 --> 00:24:45.617
They pulled the trigger, and it was like a pulse—some kind of riot control that knocked you unconscious for a couple of minutes.

00:24:45.617 --> 00:25:03.903
They just pointed it in a direction, and as soon as that beam hit an individual, it knocked them unconscious.

00:25:03.903 --> 00:25:09.662
There was no running away.

00:25:09.662 --> 00:25:19.646
It didn't kill them; it just made them pass out.

00:25:23.840 --> 00:25:33.020
This Starbucks was not here; there was a barbecue house and a Taco Bueno, but they bulldozed it.

00:25:33.020 --> 00:26:03.171
When I was with Jesus, we were standing over there by that Braum's—show them that there's a Braum's over there—an ice cream store, and all this rioting and tribulation was happening.

00:26:03.171 --> 00:26:07.170
There was lightning in the sky.

00:26:18.951 --> 00:26:19.187
I told you all there was lightning after the Rapture of the church.

00:26:19.187 --> 00:26:35.980
It was nighttime, just like it's lit up right here, but with lightning in the sky.

00:26:35.980 --> 00:26:54.590
Sometimes what you see in the spirit realm doesn't exist yet, but it's going to manifest.

00:26:54.590 --> 00:27:05.902
We're seeing it: alien visitations, the things in Miami, or unidentified objects over New York.

00:27:05.902 --> 00:27:15.720
Jesus warned this would be one of the signs of His return.

00:27:15.720 --> 00:27:26.756
This lady runs up to me and says, 'Don't you know?

00:27:26.756 --> 00:27:29.710
All the Christians are gone!

00:27:29.710 --> 00:27:36.320
' She said the aliens came and took them.

00:27:36.320 --> 00:27:48.857
Above me, lightning strikes were going all over the sky like an electric storm.

00:27:51.221 --> 00:28:01.137
I saw fires burning in a lot of buildings.

00:28:01.137 --> 00:28:06.131
People were looting and acting Godless.

00:28:08.590 --> 00:28:22.400
I want to interject something: every person wakes up with a sense of peace they don't realize they have.

00:28:22.400 --> 00:28:32.200
I call this the prayer covering of the church.

00:28:32.200 --> 00:28:56.280
When the Rapture takes place, that covering is removed, and there is total anarchy because people feel that void of peace.

00:28:56.280 --> 00:29:04.120
There's no such thing as aliens; they are demonic spirits.

00:29:04.120 --> 00:29:08.640
This is just the beginning.

00:29:11.668 --> 00:29:27.445
I really believe there is actually going to be demonic alien stuff on TV, and they're actually going to interview them.

00:29:27.445 --> 00:29:37.125
It's going to be a big deal.

00:29:37.125 --> 00:29:40.720
You're going to see a great deception.

00:29:43.153 --> 00:30:00.480
Jesus told me in 2014 they're going to talk about aliens a lot, and he told me to watch for the great deception.

00:30:12.992 --> 00:30:13.384
I saw thousands of Christians who were left here because they lived a compromising lifestyle.

00:30:13.384 --> 00:30:27.773
They had an appearance of godliness, but their hearts were far from the Lord.

00:30:27.773 --> 00:30:43.480
There were pastors who preached a watered-down grace message who were left here as punishment for preaching a lukewarm gospel.

00:30:43.480 --> 00:30:53.319
People were mad and were after those preachers, saying, 'You lied to us!

00:30:53.319 --> 00:31:18.240
' I saw one lady I knew very well from a church where I worked as a janitor; she looked up at the heavens and flipped the Lord off.

00:31:18.240 --> 00:31:21.639
Today is your day of salvation.

00:31:21.639 --> 00:31:25.795
Don't wait for tomorrow.

00:31:25.795 --> 00:31:27.039
Eternity is forever.

00:31:36.880 --> 00:31:37.151
You can either be in hell or with Jesus.

00:31:37.151 --> 00:31:41.345
Hell was made for Satan, not for you.

00:31:41.345 --> 00:31:45.399
Accept Jesus as your Lord and Savior.

00:31:45.399 --> 00:31:51.836
Say this simple prayer: 'Jesus, I'm a sinner.

00:31:51.836 --> 00:31:56.560
I ask you to come into my heart.

00:32:07.465 --> 00:32:07.840
I believe you are the Son of God.

00:32:07.840 --> 00:32:14.251
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

00:32:14.251 --> 00:32:20.053
I've messed up, but you are faithful to forgive me.

00:32:24.319 --> 00:32:27.860
I accept you as my Lord and Savior.

00:32:27.860 --> 00:32:30.434
' That's it.

00:32:35.145 --> 00:32:39.912
Get in a Bible-believing church and get your lamp full of oil.

00:32:39.912 --> 00:32:46.240
If you got saved today, let us know in the comments.

00:32:46.240 --> 00:32:54.559
Subscribe to the channel; it helps get the gospel spread through the algorithm.

00:33:00.279 --> 00:33:03.620
Father, I thank you for everyone here today.

00:33:03.620 --> 00:33:11.283
Jesus paid the price for us to walk in victory.

00:33:11.283 --> 00:33:12.159
Amen.

00:33:12.159 --> 00:33:15.439
Have a wonderful day.

00:33:15.439 --> 00:33:16.279
Bye-bye.
